SUMMARY:Welcome to the City: Santa Cruz
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Welcome to the City in Santa Cruz\, hosted in partnership with the Homeless Garden Project. The project will be held Saturday\, November 15 from 10 a.m. – 12 p.m. at the Homeless Garden Project Natural Bridges Farm (Shaffer Rd\, Santa Cruz\, CA 95060). Please register in advance to help us and our non-profit partner plan accordingly. \nProject description: \nParticipants will receive a tour of the farm and then assist with some farm tasks. \nWelcome to the City is an annual series of regional events which help alumni connect with their local UCSC community. While the program is designed with recent grads in mind\, all are welcome to participate. \nPlease contact alumni@ucsc.edu with questions.
